title: CDN Plugin
desc:
Applicable scenarios: For uploading attachments to a specified personal or company CDN source and obtaining the CDN link.
Currently supported: Alibaba Cloud √ Tencent Cloud × Qiniu Cloud ×. If you need support for other CDN sources, please join the plugin group and push the author.
ossTip: Tip: Please fill in the following Alibaba Cloud OSS configuration information

placeholder.bucket: Please fill in the bucket name
placeholder.attchment: Please select the field where the attachment is located
placeholder.link: Please select the field where the link is located

fieldSelectedTip: Tip: Please select the attachment and link fields

toast.lackRequiredInfo: Please fill in the required information
